uations where you took initiative or displayed an entrepreneurial approach.", "What new engineering specialty skills have you developed during the past year?", "Tell me about your greatest success in using logic to solve an engineering problem.", "Give me an example of something that you have learned from a mistake that you made on a job at a client site.", "What do you get out of engineering that you couldn’t get from any other kind of work?", "What was your professional development plan for the past two years?", "Tell me about a time when you surpassed all expectations by going “above and beyond” for a client.", "Do you have any patents? If so, tell me about them. If not, is it something you see yourself pursuing and why or why not?", "Describe your ideal boss.", "Share an example of how you have applied your skills to on-site work."]

